//"The clear skies, the lure of the open road, it's perfect!" -- Tana
You grew up traveling, whether with family or other companions. You've visited many communities, seen many interesting sights, and heard many fascinating tales. These experiences let you understand and embrace difference.
You've learned to approach situations through openness.

